                                "titre": "Make another cut in the same half buckle, a few millimeters away from the cut.",
                                "sous_etapes": []
                            },
                            {
                                "titre": "The intention is to remove enough plastic so you can slip material through the gap with relative ease, but not so much that the material can too easily slip out again when in use.",
